1. What was the hardest part?

The hardest part was saving the data to a file and loading it back into the program.

2. What would you improve with another hour?

I would add more features like deleting media, editing items, and filtering by type.

3. Did you use AI tools? If so, how?

Yes. I used AI to help explain Java syntax and help dubug the file saving and loading process.

4. Tell us one specific design decision you made

I decided to make the project a simple console app so I could focus on the main features.

5. Tell us one specific tradeoff you accepted

I used simple ArrayLists instead of more advanced classes to keep the code easier to understand.

6. Tell us one known limitation or bug

The program can crash if the save file is changed or formatted incorrectly.
